SUB_W13_WRLD_BOFO_INITIAL_000_CUT_000_01.text:
We need a base of operations more than a river;
hopefully there's someone living around here
who can point us in the right direction.

SUB_W13_EVAR_BOFO_ROUTE2_DIVING_000_CUT_.text:
That's a long time to be left alone;
you must have been incredibly lonely.
We'd be happy to chat a bit, if you like.

SUB_W13_EVAR_BOFO_ROUTE2_FERRY_000_CUT_0.text:
Well? What have you brought me?
Please say you have copper wire;
I desperately need it for my motors.

SUB_W13_EVAR_BOFO_ROUTE3_FERRY_000_CUT_0.text:
Actually, this ship might not have sank;
the ocean could've dried up around it.
There's no way for us to know.
